  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>This hotel is offered on either half board or all inclusive.</p>
<p>The half board offering consists of breakfast and dinner. Drinks are not included.</p>
<p>Each morning a continental buffet breakfast is served with additional hot options.</p>
<p>Hot drinks and sweet treats and cakes are available throughout the hotel throughout the day. There are coffee machines on each floor of the hotel.</p>
<p>The evening meals are served buffet style which is influenced by world cuisine. </p>
<p>Alternatively you can upgrade to the "all inclusive" package which further enhances your stay with breakfast, lunch, dinner and drinks included. Unlimited soft drinks, hot drinks, beer and wine in the hotel from 10am-10pm and between 6-10pm a selection of other alcoholic drinks are also available. The "all inclusive" option can be pre-booked with your holiday, just pick up the all inclusive package if booking online.</p>
<p>Christmas and New Year gala dinners included.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
