  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Ibiza is set back from the resort centre, giving you wonderful views across the mountains and resort. The rooms combine warm and wooden Alpine décor with modern amenities, plus there is an indoor pool and wellness facilities included in your stay - this is a great choice for skiers and non skiers alike.</p>
<h2>Inspired by pop culture</h2>
<p>The Hotel Ibiza is furnished in a traditional alpine design, and has an eclectic and fun homage to pop culture; a young <em>Madonna</em> and <em>The Rolling Stones</em> are but a few of the famous names embellishing the hotel walls and lounge. </p>
<h2>Fantastic views</h2>
<p><span>Enjoy your morning coffee on the south facing sun soaked terrace with wonderful views </span>of the Parc National des Ecrins.<span> Most of the rooms also have views of the La Muzelle summit, you will never get bored of the breath-taking view here. </span></p>
<h2><span>Relax and unwind</span></h2>
<p><span>After a day of exploring Les 2 Alpes, make the most of the hotels wellness area. Take a dip in the indoor heated pool or relax on the sun loungers which have fantastic views of the surrounding mountains. Soak your muscles in the hot tub or relax in the sauna or steam room. </span><span>Treat yourself to a massage or treatment which are available for an additional supplement. </span></p>
<p><span>If you still have some energy after a day on the mountain, the hotel also has a fitness room available for you to use which has a variety of weights and machines. </span></p>]]></description>
