  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard North Facing Room </strong>are around 18m²,  sleeps two people, and have a north facing view. These rooms are available available for sole occupancy.</p>
<p><strong>Superior South Facing Rooms </strong>are more spacious at around 25m², sleeps two people and have a balcony with a south facing mountain view. These rooms are also available for sole occupancy. </p>
<p><strong>Duplex suite </strong> sleeps up to four people and are around 40m². The duplex suites are set over two floors with a double sofa  bed in the living room and twin or double beds on the mezzanine level. The duplex suites have a balcony with south facing mountain views.</p>
<p><strong>Large Double Room </strong>sleeps <span>two adults and a child up to 18 years old on the sofa bed (two small children may sleep on the sofa bed which is around 120cm wide). The rooms are around 25m² and have a north facing view.</span></p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>All rooms have double or twin beds (please specify preference when booking)</li>
<li>View with mountain views</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Free WiFi</li>
<li>Bath with shower head attachment or shower room</li>
<li>Hair dryer</li>
<li>Toiletries</li>
<li>Towels</li>
<li>Bed linen</li>
<li>Coffee machine (on request)</li>
<li>iPod docking station (on request)</li>
<li>Beds are made on arrival</li>
<li>Daily house keeping is included</li>
<li>Cots available on request. All rooms can fit a cot except Standarerd Rooms.</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
